{
  "texts": [
    "These topics, characterized by their most relevant documents and keywords identified through c-TF-IDF, serve as the input for Llama 2(2), following our prompt template.",
    "The template is populated with the top 5 most relevant documents and the top 10 keywords for each topic, guiding Llama 2(2) to generate a short, precise label for the topic.To enrich our topic representations, we incorporated additional models alongside Llama 2(2).",
    "Specifically, we utilized c-TF-IDF for the primary representation and supplemented it with KeyBERT(82), MMR (Maximal Marginal Relevance), and Llama 2(2) for multi-faceted topic insights.",
    "This approach allows for a comprehensive view of each topic from multiple analytical perspectives.",
    "With the models and methodologies in place, we proceeded to train our topic model by supplying BERTopic (76) with the designated sub-models.The training process involved fitting the model to our dataset and transforming the data to extract topics."
  ]
}